Definition: a Christian sacrament signifying spiritual cleansing and rebirth
Example: most churches baptize infants but some insist on adult baptism
Synonyms: adj, pert, baptismal, noun, person, baptist, verb, communication, baptize, baptise, sacrament, a, Christian, signifying, spiritual, cleansing, and, rebirth, most, churches, infants, but, some, insist, on, adult
Category: noun.act
